Backend Integration and API Development
Objective:
Integrate backend services and APIs into the app.
Activities:
1.
Days 19-21 : Backend Services Introduction
Learn about backend services and REST APIs.
Explore tools like Firebase for backend integration.
2.
Days 22-24 : API Integration
Set up API calls to fetch and send data.
Implement data handling and parsing in Android Studio.
3.
Days 25-27 : Error Handling and Debugging
Implement error handling for API requests.
Debug and resolve any issues with data integration.
Deliverables:
GitHub repository updated with backend integration and API functionality.
LinkedIn post detailing the backend integration process and challenges faced.
